parameters: Umi: "Inside here... is the divine body of Mear?"
Lutecia: "Yes... With this, I can regain my power and memories..."
Kru: "You froze all of a sudden, you scared me."
Luitesia: "No, I'm not sick. Don't you two... remember anything?"
Luitesia: "No... it's nothing... I was just... a little happy, that's all."

Luitesia: "Now... Kru. There exists a causality centered around you in
time."

Luitesia: "Because of that, you might have experienced some hardships...
but maybe it was all for this moment..."
Luitesia: "Now, I will consolidate all your causality."

Luitesia: "All of time... the power of Kru from every world... gather
here..."
Kru: "This is... like the ghost I saw once..."

Luitesia: "All the emotions, all the curses, all the anger, all the
sadness..."

Luitesia: "To eradicate the root cause of all causality, lend us your
strength..."
Kru: "Yeah... *pant* *pant*... just a bit... shocked, that's all..."
Luitesia: "How about it, Kru? Do you feel anything?"

Kru: "Yeah... I guess... It's not so much that I feel stronger, but
everything feels lighter..."

Luitesia: "With this, Kru will no longer travel back in time. In other
words, this timeline will be our last challenge."
Luitesia: "Hehehe... Now, let's return to the village."

Luitesia: "Damn... Since the sacred object is gone... the monsters have
come this far..."
Umi: "What should we do... we're surrounded..."
Kru: "Ah... I just moved a bit faster, that's all."
Kru: "Now... let's go to the village..."
